\q1 \w and|strong="H4430"\w* let it live \w with|strong="H6903"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* animals \w in|strong="H4437"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* grass \w of|strong="H4437"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* land.
\q1 
\v 16 Let \w his|strong="H1768"\w* mind \w be|strong="H8160"\w* altered \w from|strong="H1768"\w* \w that|strong="H1768"\w* \w of|strong="H4430"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* human being,
\q1 \w and|strong="H6032"\w* let \w an|strong="H4430"\w* animal’s mind \w be|strong="H8160"\w* given \w to|strong="H4430"\w* him,
\q1 \w and|strong="H6032"\w* let \w seven|strong="H2298"\w* periods \w of|strong="H4430"\w* \w time|strong="H8160"\w* go by \w for|strong="H1768"\w* him.
\q1 
\v 17 \w This|strong="H3606"\w* announcement \w is|strong="H1768"\w* by \w the|strong="H3606"\w* decree \w of|strong="H1768"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* sentinels;
\q1 \w this|strong="H3606"\w* decision \w is|strong="H1768"\w* by \w the|strong="H3606"\w* pronouncement \w of|strong="H1768"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* holy ones,
\q1 \w so|strong="H1768"\w* \w that|strong="H1768"\w* \w those|strong="H1768"\w* \w who|strong="H1768"\w* \w are|strong="H1768"\w* alive may understand
\q1 \w that|strong="H1768"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* Most High \w has|strong="H1768"\w* authority over human kingdoms,
\q1 \w and|strong="H8065"\w* \w he|strong="H1768"\w* bestows them on \w whomever|strong="H1768"\w* \w he|strong="H1768"\w* wishes.
\q1 \w He|strong="H1768"\w* establishes over them \w even|strong="H1768"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* lowliest \w of|strong="H1768"\w* human beings.’
\p 
\v 18 “\w This|strong="H3606"\w* \w is|strong="H3606"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* dream \w that|strong="H3606"\w* I, King Nebuchadnezzar, saw. Now you, Belteshazzar, declare its interpretation, \w for|strong="H4203"\w* \w none|strong="H3606"\w* \w of|strong="H3606"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* wise men \w in|strong="H1753"\w* my kingdom are able \w to|strong="H8065"\w* make known \w to|strong="H8065"\w* me \w the|strong="H3606"\w* interpretation. \w But|strong="H3606"\w* you can \w do|strong="H8065"\w* so, \w for|strong="H4203"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* spirit \w of|strong="H3606"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* holy gods \w is|strong="H3606"\w* \w in|strong="H1753"\w* you.”
\s1 Daniel Interprets Nebuchadnezzar’s Dream
\p 
\v 19 \w Then|strong="H4430"\w* Daniel (\w whose|strong="H1768"\w* name \w is|strong="H1768"\w* \w also|strong="H4430"\w* Belteshazzar) \w was|strong="H4430"\w* upset \w for|strong="H1768"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* brief time; \w his|strong="H1768"\w* thoughts \w were|strong="H1768"\w* alarming him. \w The|strong="H1768"\w* \w king|strong="H4430"\w* said, “Belteshazzar, don’t let \w the|strong="H1768"\w* dream \w and|strong="H4430"\w* its interpretation alarm \w you|strong="H1768"\w*.” \w But|strong="H1768"\w* Belteshazzar replied, “Sir, if only \w the|strong="H1768"\w* dream \w were|strong="H1768"\w* \w for|strong="H1768"\w* \w your|strong="H1768"\w* enemies \w and|strong="H4430"\w* its interpretation applied \w to|strong="H4430"\w* \w your|strong="H1768"\w* adversaries!
\v 20 \w The|strong="H5922"\w* tree \w that|strong="H1768"\w* \w you|strong="H1768"\w* \w saw|strong="H2370"\w* \w that|strong="H1768"\w* grew large \w and|strong="H4430"\w* strong, \w whose|strong="H1768"\w* top reached \w to|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* \w sky|strong="H8065"\w*, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w which|strong="H1768"\w* \w could|strong="H1768"\w* \w be|strong="H5732"\w* \w seen|strong="H2370"\w* \w in|strong="H5922"\w* all \w the|strong="H5922"\w* land,
\v 21 \w whose|strong="H1768"\w* foliage \w was|strong="H4430"\w* attractive \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w its|strong="H6591"\w* fruit plentiful, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w from|strong="H1768"\w* \w which|strong="H1768"\w* \w there|strong="H1768"\w* \w was|strong="H4430"\w* food available \w for|strong="H5922"\w* all, under \w whose|strong="H1768"\w* branches wild animals used \w to|strong="H5922"\w* live, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w in|strong="H5922"\w* \w whose|strong="H1768"\w* branches birds \w of|strong="H4430"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* sky used \w to|strong="H5922"\w* nest –
\v 22 \w it|strong="H5922"\w* \w is|strong="H1768"\w* \w you|strong="H1768"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* king! \w For|strong="H5922"\w* \w you|strong="H1768"\w* \w have|strong="H1934"\w* become great \w and|strong="H8065"\w* strong. \w Your|strong="H5922"\w* greatness \w is|strong="H1768"\w* \w such|strong="H1768"\w* \w that|strong="H1768"\w* \w it|strong="H5922"\w* reaches \w to|strong="H5922"\w* \w heaven|strong="H8065"\w*, \w and|strong="H8065"\w* \w your|strong="H5922"\w* \w authority|strong="H7990"\w* \w to|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* ends \w of|strong="H4481"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* earth.
\v 23 \w As|strong="H1768"\w* \w for|strong="H1768"\w* \w the|strong="H4481"\w* king seeing \w a|strong="H3068"\w* holy sentinel coming down \w from|strong="H4481"\w* \w heaven|strong="H8065"\w* \w and|strong="H8065"\w* saying, ‘Chop down \w the|strong="H4481"\w* tree \w and|strong="H8065"\w* destroy \w it|strong="H4481"\w*, \w but|strong="H1768"\w* \w leave|strong="H7662"\w* \w its|strong="H3046"\w* taproot \w in|strong="H4437"\w* \w the|strong="H4481"\w* ground, with \w a|strong="H3068"\w* band \w of|strong="H4481"\w* iron \w and|strong="H8065"\w* bronze around \w it|strong="H4481"\w*, surrounded \w by|strong="H4481"\w* \w the|strong="H4481"\w* grass \w of|strong="H4481"\w* \w the|strong="H4481"\w* field. Let \w it|strong="H4481"\w* become damp with \w the|strong="H4481"\w* dew \w of|strong="H4481"\w* \w the|strong="H4481"\w* \w sky|strong="H8065"\w*, \w and|strong="H8065"\w* let \w it|strong="H4481"\w* live with \w the|strong="H4481"\w* wild animals, until seven periods \w of|strong="H4481"\w* time go \w by|strong="H4481"\w* \w for|strong="H1768"\w* \w him|strong="H4481"\w*’ –
\v 24 \w this|strong="H5922"\w* is \w the|strong="H5922"\w* interpretation, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w king|strong="H4430"\w*! \w It|strong="H5922"\w* is \w the|strong="H5922"\w* decision \w of|strong="H4430"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* Most High \w that|strong="H2006"\w* \w this|strong="H5922"\w* \w has|strong="H4430"\w* happened \w to|strong="H5922"\w* \w my|strong="H5922"\w* lord \w the|strong="H5922"\w* \w king|strong="H4430"\w*.
\v 25 \w You|strong="H5922"\w* \w will|strong="H3606"\w* be driven from human society, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w you|strong="H5922"\w* \w will|strong="H3606"\w* live \w with|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* wild animals. \w You|strong="H5922"\w* \w will|strong="H3606"\w* be fed grass like oxen, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w you|strong="H5922"\w* \w will|strong="H3606"\w* become damp \w with|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* dew \w of|strong="H4430"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* sky. Seven periods \w of|strong="H4430"\w* time \w will|strong="H3606"\w* pass by \w for|strong="H5922"\w* \w you|strong="H5922"\w*, \w before|strong="H5922"\w* \w you|strong="H5922"\w* understand \w that|strong="H3606"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* Most High \w is|strong="H3606"\w* ruler \w over|strong="H5922"\w* human kingdoms \w and|strong="H4430"\w* gives \w them|strong="H5922"\w* \w to|strong="H5922"\w* whomever \w he|strong="H5020"\w* wishes.
